modName: Dwarven Black Bow of Fate Craftable and Enchantable SE
summary: A simple mod that allows to craft Dwarven Black Bow and enchant it. Black Bow is in Dwarven section in blacksmith and can be found on the floor near the original Black Bow of Fate pedestal in Kagrumez.
descriptionHtml: I made this mod because I really like model of dwarven black bow, but there was no way to get the enchantable one. So, now it is :)
author: Nimick
